---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Evidence before capital"
  description="We help quantitative traders identify which public strategies still work — and which have already died. Independent research for systematic traders."
>
  <section style="margin-top:3rem;margin-bottom:2rem;">
    <h1 style="font-size:2.5rem;letter-spacing:-0.04em;line-height:1.15;">Evidence before capital.</h1>
    <p style="font-size:1.2rem;max-width:600px;margin-bottom:2rem;color:var(--color-text);">
      We help quantitative traders identify which public strategies still work — and which have already died.
    </p>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <a href="/research" style="display:inline-block;padding:0.7rem 1.8rem;background:var(--color-text);color:#fff;text-decoration:none;border-radius:6px;font-size:1rem;font-weight:500;">Get Free Report</a>
      <span style="display:inline-block;padding:0.7rem 1.5rem;color:var(--color-muted);border:1px solid var(--color-border);border-radius:6px;font-size:0.9375rem;">Founding Report (Soon)</span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <hr />

  <section>
    <h2>Why Alpha Factory Research</h2>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:1.5rem;margin-top:1rem;">
      <div><h3 style="margin-top:0;">Reality Check</h3><p>We test public trading strategies against real market data. Most fail. We publish which ones.</p></div>
      <div><h3 style="margin-top:0;">Forward Evidence</h3><p>We collect prospective paper-trading evidence before any capital is deployed. No backtest-alone claims.</p></div>
      <div><h3 style="margin-top:0;">Cost-aware Validation</h3><p>Fees, slippage, and concentration analysis. Gross profit is not enough.</p></div>
      <div><h3 style="margin-top:0;">No Signal Selling</h3><p>We publish research. We do not sell trading signals, investment advice, or portfolio management.</p></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <hr />

  <section>
    <h2>FAQ</h2>
    <p><strong>Do you provide trading signals?</strong><br/>No.</p>
    <p><strong>Do you guarantee profits?</strong><br/>No.</p>
    <p><strong>What do you sell?</strong><br/>Research.</p>
  </section>

  <hr />

  <section style="text-align:center;padding:2rem 0;">
    <h2>Get the Founding Report</h2>
    <p style="max-width:500px;margin:0 auto 1.5rem;">The first report covers which public crypto trading strategies survived independent validation — and why most failed. Join the waitlist.</p>
    <a href="/research" id="buy-button" style="display:inline-block;padding:0.7rem 2rem;background:var(--color-text);color:#fff;text-decoration:none;border-radius:6px;font-size:1rem;font-weight:500;">Coming Soon</a>
    <p style="font-size:0.8rem;margin-top:1rem;color:var(--color-muted);">Payment processing via Lemon Squeezy. No account required.</p>
  </section>
</Base>
